12.title: Clip: Flo's Cafe

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

12.plot: Help your young Cars fan develop fine motor skills building Lightning McQueen, Cruz Ramirez and Mack, and when they've all finished hanging out at Flo's V8 Café, your child can fuel them all up at the gas pump. They'll have endless fun driving Lightning McQueen up the ramp into Mack's trailer and heading off to his next race. Lego 10846.

13.title: Clip: Lightning McQueen Speed Launcer

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

13.plot: Join in the exciting Disney Pixar Cars 3 racing world with Lightning McQueen's Speed Launcher, featuring a race leader board, starting ramp and a launch function with a red button. Includes a simple guide to build and play, and bigger pieces help build confidence in younger kids. Lego 10730.

14.title: Clip: Cruz Ramirez Race Simulator

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

14.plot: Be part of the exciting Disney.Pixar Cars 3 racing world with Cruz Ramirez and her Race Simulator, featuring a rotating screen, ramp and turbine fan to test Cruz' racing skills. Includes a simple guide to build and play, and bigger pieces help build confidence in younger kids. Lego 10731.

15.title: Clip: Guido and Luigi's Pit Stop

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

15.plot: Join in the Disney.Pixar Cars 3 fun at Guido and Luigi's Pit Stop, featuring an air hose, fuel can and spare tire accessory elements and a number 95 pit sign. Includes a simple guide to build and play, and bigger pieces help build confidence in younger kids. Lego 10732.

16.title: Clip: Mater's Junkyard

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

16.plot: Join Mater in his Easy to Build junkyard as he chats with Lightning McQueen on the video screen, featuring a movable crane and Tow Mater sign. Use the crane to lift the assorted car parts out of the box and attach them to the build-able tow truck, and have fun testing them on this lovable Disney.Pixar Cars 3 character. Lego 10733.

17.title: Clip: Willy's Butte Speed Training

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

17.plot: Start your engines in this high-octane Willy's Butte Speed Training LEGO® Juniors play set, featuring a detachable speed radar trailer, roadblock with breakable barriers, spinning Radiator Springs road sign and other accessories to ramp up the Disney.Pixar Cars 3 fun. Includes a simple guide to build and play, and bigger pieces help build confidence in younger kids. Lego 10742.

18.title: Clip: Smokey's Garage

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

18.plot: Give Lightning McQueen a service in Smokey's Garage after a hard day training on the racetrack. Drive the car up the ramp, change the tires, pick the tool accessories from the cabinet and role-play endless Disney.Pixar Cars 3 scenes with this fun Lego Juniors set. Includes a simple guide to build and play, and bigger pieces help build confidence in younger kids. Lego 10743.

19.title: Clip: Thunder Hollow Crazy 8 Race

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

19.plot: Throw out the racing rule book in this action-packed LEGO Juniors set, featuring an Easy to Build 'Fritter Time' road sign with breakable barriers, ramps, flaming tires and assorted demolition derby accessories to set the pulse racing of any Disney.Pixar Cars 3 fan. Includes a simple guide to build and play, and bigger pieces help build confidence in younger kids. Lego 10744.

20.title: Clip: Lightning McQueen Ultimate Build

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

20.plot: Race on the world stage with the Ultimate Build Lightning McQueen. Lightning McQueen is strutting his stuff on the start line of the World Grand Prix. He's geared up and ready to roll with golden racing rims. Guido is cheering him on from the pits and the crowd is roaring. Help him to finish in fast and flashy style. Lego 8484.

21.title: Clip: Florida 500 Final Race

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Cars - Artifex (TV Series 2014–2017)

21.plot: Start your engines and take part in the exciting Florida 500 Final Race from Disney.Pixar Cars 3, featuring an Easy to Build crew chief's stand with raising red and green race flags and Start/Finish line arch, track side barriers and a winners' podium with checkered flags and a trophy. Includes a simple guide to build and play, and bigger pieces help build confidence in younger kids. Lego 10745.

imdb.plot outline: Cars is set in an alternate universe where every character is a vehicle of various sorts, whether that be automobile, aircraft or watercraft. The film focuses on a rookie race car named Lightning McQueen who discovers the lost town of Radiator Springs on his way to the biggest race of his life.
